    "147144132": {
      "title": "The EQ Difference. A Powerful Plan for Putting Emotional Intelligence to Work",
      "abstract": "The EQ Difference offers practical tips and suggestions for developing emotional intelligence and reaping its benefits in any work environmentThe book helps professionals at all levels understand how emotions can have a profound effect on performance, values, and relationships in the workplace. Features practical self-assessment exercises and team-oriented tools to leverage EQ individually and in groups."
